align=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ToVN Rotation agreement/rules</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>    So my goals and ambitions as a small guild leader with alliances is not as important as NB, Tindi or BoTS? Or other guilds that are capable of taking these mobs alone, their goals and ambitions dont mean @#%$ because they are not that grand? Thanks for clearing up how you feel about smaller guilds and their members.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Not at all.  I was stating history.  The fact is and was that these four guilds saw the whole thing as a package deal and it wasn't that important for them to consider those two (and they didn't) seperately because their goal was clearing ToVN, not simply farming Ikatair and Eashen for items.  No one thought that there would be a guild that would be content with killing Ikatair and Eashen only and not clearing ToVN.  Because this wasn't imagined, the main concern was having fair access to those mobs so they were lumped in with ToVN for convenience so a guild wouldn't have to make multiple trips to ToVN just to go back and reclear those two mobs.  Do it all in one trip and get out of there and do something else.<br>
<br>
Remember this agreement was made a very long time ago and the server is nothing like it is now.  We made an agreement that fit the times, and has worked to this day and is now only in question because I posted the details to it.  As far as I know, there have be *no* guilds other than the ones who have cleared ToVN who have even attempted Ikatair and Eashen, much less killed them so the point is kind of moot other than an academic discussion right now.<br>
<br>
Vorth: Until someone else (who isn't on the ToVN rotation) kills Ikatair/Eashen (no one else has as far as I know), by convention, the rotation as it exists isn't in dispute. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ugrommofbots.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gromm of BotS</A> at: 9/16/02 2:41:47 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#00FFFF>- </font><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency>The Rathe Travel Agency Board</a><font color=#00FFFF> - </font><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50>General</a> <font color=#00FFFF> - </font><a href="http://www.jakefitch.com/rta/Calendar.asp">The Rathe Calendar</a><font color=#00FFFF> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.0.8<br>Copyright ©1999-2002 ezboard, Inc.<br>Accelerated By <a href=http://www.wbs.com/ezboard.html>JXEL</a></center></body></html>  

